{"tid":458573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世界各國　球迷噓國歌　時有發生","createTime":"2017-11-05T04:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T05:17:38.000Z","uid":47714,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5e376d2f9a92984bce8f71d99d98e229e3e2acb7","tid":458573,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:20:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171011/20179086\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171011%2F20179086&d=e1BInvnWR2pTlA6dXv6sI7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=acb7aa0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171011%2F20179086&h=e756385b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171011/20179086</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171011/large/15082101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171011%2Flarge%2F15082101.jpg&h=31af73b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】噓國歌並非罕見，在歐洲球壇時有發生。近期鬧得熱烘烘的西班牙加泰羅尼亞獨立事件，加泰地區最具代表性的球隊巴塞隆拿，亦曾因球迷噓國歌被罰。美國則有美式足球賽球員在奏國歌時單膝下跪而惹爭議。<br />\n<br />\n2015年5月上演的西班牙盃決賽，由巴塞隆拿對畢爾包，在華倫西亞的中立場上對壘。巴塞所處的加泰羅尼亞獨立聲音不斷，而畢爾包則是西班牙另一自治區巴斯克地區的球會，當地分離分子一度令馬德里政府非常頭痛，到近年才轉趨沉寂。兩年前的西班牙盃決賽，賽前按例會奏西班牙國歌，隨即被巴畢兩隊球迷狂噓。<br />\n<br />\n蘇格蘭隊繡罌粟花被罰<br />\n<br />\n西班牙國家反暴力委員會當年7月處分巴塞與畢爾包，兩隊分別被罰66,000歐元（約60.8萬港元）及18,000歐元（約16.6萬港元），連西班牙足總亦受連累，遭罰款12,300歐元（約11.3萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n在國際球壇，英國分成英格蘭、蘇格蘭、威爾斯及北愛爾蘭國家足球代表隊。<br />\n由去年9月展開，剛於周二結束的2018世盃外圍賽歐洲區分組賽，英格蘭與蘇格蘭被編成同一組，兩隊在去年11月首次碰頭，英格蘭在主場以3:0擊敗蘇格蘭一仗，便有作客的蘇格蘭球迷，在奏英格蘭國歌時報以噓聲，加上蘇格蘭球員在該仗的球衣繡上了罌粟花標誌，事後被歐洲足協罰款16,000鎊（約16.5萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n今年3月兩隊在蘇格蘭的咸普頓公園球場再交手，再有蘇球迷噓國歌，結果被歐洲足協再罰4,000鎊（約4.1萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n趁球賽前奏國歌時表達不滿不限於球迷，球員也可以借國歌發揮。在美國，國家美式足球聯盟（NFL）球員多次在奏國歌時單膝跪地抗議，美國總統特朗普嚴詞干預也未能制止。"},{"pid":"442937c2c07f3be008eff4b8c62df1bf87daa9b9","tid":458573,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:28:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/121652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F121652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0c579d86&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8741e0eb0d56c0209f2c6086f1ceaa192abdab04","tid":458573,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:51:59.000Z","msg":"Italian fans begin to boo French national anthem<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B8yv4_gGMKc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DB8yv4_gGMKc&d=e1BInvnWR2pTlA6dXv6sI7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=2448bd48\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B8yv4_gGMKc</a>"},{"pid":"03c2a60c1a3d180461711d7fa6fae3de1d5fc510","tid":458573,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:52:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">歡迎極右派政治家通過嚴格標準上榜</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><ins>細字濃縮試用版</ins><br />\n經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：三色貓、法國佬巫斯義、極右派政治家、群龍共舞、優美開始、JR、RedBaron、Gladiclus、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據一：五毛一見字眼空群而出</ins><br />\n連狗對五毛問題視而不見、置若罔聞，與全連登作對<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451623\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451623</a><br />\n【枕戈待旦】有關被連狗封鎖禁言之嚴正聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/442843\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/442843</a><br />\n刺刀捅向習匪頭 鏟平地獄鬼國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/439819\