li-anthem-give-Nazi-salute-at-world-cup-qualifier-467197&d=e1BInvnWR2pTlA6dXv6sI7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=25387cc9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jpost.com/Israel-News/Sports/Italian-fans-boo-Israeli-anthem-give-Nazi-salute-at-world-cup-qualifier-467197</a>"},{"pid":"d8605671fe49b3eee6ebabf1e0e2a2e5c6ae14bd","tid":458573,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T05:05:27.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=trY0V_G0LzUC&amp;pg=PA72&amp;lpg=PA72&amp;dq=&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=UYIF5GCZZa&amp;sig=B_hYLnbshQQE2FDeJ6IFZ-Nvyk8&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjah4mk06bXAhWMF5QKHdfnCR0Q6AEIRzAI#v=onepage\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com.hk%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DtrY0V_G0LzUC%26pg%3DPA72%26lpg%3DPA72%26dq%3D%26source%3Dbl%26ots%3DUYIF5GCZZa%26sig%3DB_hYLnbshQQE2FDeJ6IFZ-Nvyk8%26hl%3Dzh-TW%26sa%3DX%26ved%3D0ahUKEwjah4mk06bXAhWMF5QKHdfnCR0Q6AEIRzAI%23v%3Donepage&d=e1BInvnWR2pTlA6dXv6sI7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7ec607b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=trY0V_G0LzUC&amp;pg=PA72&amp;lpg=PA72&amp;dq=&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=UYIF5GCZZa&amp;sig=B_hYLnbshQQE2FDeJ6IFZ-Nvyk8&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjah4mk06bXAhWMF5QKHdfnCR0Q6AEIRzAI#v=onepage</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\nWhen Argentina met Brazil in Turin, two weeks later, the Turin Fans(of Juventus FC and Torino) behaved in the same way. They booed the Argentinian national anthem and supported Brazil"},{"pid":"8885bcbf6276dc031b5ba41b65686d2d3fb96982","tid":458573,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T05:12:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/football/2007/nov/21/minutebyminute.sport\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ffootball%2F2007%2Fnov%2F21%2Fminutebyminute.sport&d=e1BInvnWR2pTlA6dXv6sI7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=b8b4ce0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/football/20